rows.label: xs33680100_MSG0010
rows.name: Oh, look who it is. Glad you're unharmed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33680100_MSG0020
rows.name: If I'd had a Skell, I could've at least done something...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33680100_MSG0030
rows.name:
But the way things are,
I was stuck twiddling my thumbs, pretty much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33680100_MSG0040
rows.name:
It's a strange old place...
You want back into the fray, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33680100_MSG0050
rows.name: Okay. I'm with you all the way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33680100_MSG0060
rows.name:
Leesh is out there waiting for me.
Let's take this guy off his high horse, and go home.[ST:wait ]
